The paper discusses the development of a reputation system for different environments such as social networks, financial ecosystems, and marketplaces. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of social networks (cs.SI), cybernetics (cs.CY), databases (cs.DB), social and information networks (cs.SOC), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as these sub-categories are relevant to the topics discussed in the paper.
